    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I have a branch started with:\n\n``` c#\n    public struct PipType\n    {\n        public readonly string Sequence;\n        public readonly float Fill = 0;\n    }\n```\n\nwhere `Sequence` is the pip sequence to use and `(int)((sequence_frame_count - 1) * Fill)` is the sequence frame to allow partial fill pips.\n"
